[
  {
    "id": "1",
    "text": "For God so loved the world that he gave his one and only Son, that whoever believes in him shall not perish but have eternal life.",
    "reference": "John 3:16",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1448375240586-882707db888b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "2",
    "text": "I can do all this through him who gives me strength.",
    "reference": "Philippians 4:13",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506318137071-a8e063b4bec0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "3",
    "text": "The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing.",
    "reference": "Psalm 23:1",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1433086966358-54859d0ed716?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "4",
    "text": "But God demonstrates his own love for us in this: While we were still sinners, Christ died for us.",
    "reference": "Romans 5:8",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501630834273-4b5604d2ee31?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "5",
    "text": "Love is patient, love is kind. It does not envy, it does not boast, it is not proud.",
    "reference": "1 Corinthians 13:4",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472214103451-9374bd1c798e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "6",
    "text": "But those who hope in the Lord will renew their strength. They will soar on wings like eagles; they will run and not grow weary.",
    "reference": "Isaiah 40:31",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "7",
    "text": "Be strong and courageous. Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged, for the Lord your God will be with you wherever you go.",
    "reference": "Joshua 1:9",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "8",
    "text": "Do not be anxious about anything, but in every situation, by prayer and petition, present your requests to God.",
    "reference": "Philippians 4:6",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509316785289-025f5b846b35?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "9",
    "text": "Come to me, all you who are weary and burdened, and I will give you rest.",
    "reference": "Matthew 11:28",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518531933037-91b2f5f229cc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "10",
    "text": "Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding; in all your ways submit to him, and he will make your paths straight.",
    "reference": "Proverbs 3:5-6",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519681393784-d120267933ba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/nature.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "11",
    "text": "The Lord is close to the brokenhearted and saves those who are crushed in spirit.",
    "reference": "Psalm 34:18",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500534314209-a25ddb2bd429?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/sea.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "12",
    "text": "And we know that in all things God works for the good of those who love him, who have been called according to his purpose.",
    "reference": "Romans 8:28",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470770841072-f978cf4d019e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "13",
    "text": "Greater love has no one than this: to lay down one's life for one's friends.",
    "reference": "John 15:13",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490730141103-6cac27aaab94?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "14",
    "text": "For I know the plans I have for you, declares the Lord, plans to prosper you and not to harm you, plans to give you hope and a future.",
    "reference": "Jeremiah 29:11",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504701954957-2010ec3bcec1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "15",
    "text": "Be still, and know that I am God; I will be exalted among the nations, I will be exalted in the earth.",
    "reference": "Psalm 46:10",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501854140801-50d01698950b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/nature.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "16",
    "text": "No, in all these things we are more than conquerors through him who loved us.",
    "reference": "Romans 8:37",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "17",
    "text": "Above all, love each other deeply, because love covers over a multitude of sins.",
    "reference": "1 Peter 4:8",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518199266791-5375a83190b7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "18",
    "text": "Cast all your anxiety on him because he cares for you.",
    "reference": "1 Peter 5:7",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505118380757-91f5f5632de0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/sea.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "19",
    "text": "The Lord your God is with you, the Mighty Warrior who saves. He will take great delight in you; in his love he will no longer rebuke you, but will rejoice over you with singing.",
    "reference": "Zephaniah 3:17",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518199266791-5375a83190b7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "20",
    "text": "I have told you these things, so that in me you may have peace. In this world you will have trouble. But take heart! I have overcome the world.",
    "reference": "John 16:33",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519681393784-d120267933ba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "21",
    "text": "Even though I walk through the darkest valley, I will fear no evil, for you are with me; your rod and your staff, they comfort me.",
    "reference": "Psalm 23:4",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1448375240586-882707db888b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "22",
    "text": "Dear friends, let us love one another, for love comes from God. Everyone who loves has been born of God and knows God.",
    "reference": "1 John 4:7",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472214103451-9374bd1c798e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "23",
    "text": "The Lord is my light and my salvation — whom shall I fear? The Lord is the stronghold of my life — of whom shall I be afraid?",
    "reference": "Psalm 27:1",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506318137071-a8e063b4bec0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/nature.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "24",
    "text": "He heals the brokenhearted and binds up their wounds.",
    "reference": "Psalm 147:3",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500534314209-a25ddb2bd429?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "25",
    "text": "And now these three remain: faith, hope and love. But the greatest of these is love.",
    "reference": "1 Corinthians 13:13",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490730141103-6cac27aaab94?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "26",
    "text": "Finally, be strong in the Lord and in his mighty power.",
    "reference": "Ephesians 6:10",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "27",
    "text": "God is our refuge and strength, an ever-present help in trouble.",
    "reference": "Psalm 46:1",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/sea.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "28",
    "text": "Peace I leave with you; my peace I give you. I do not give to you as the world gives. Do not let your hearts be troubled and do not be afraid.",
    "reference": "John 14:27",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501854140801-50d01698950b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "29",
    "text": "How great is the love the Father has lavished on us, that we should be called children of God!",
    "reference": "1 John 3:1",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518199266791-5375a83190b7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "30",
    "text": "I sought the Lord, and he answered me; he delivered me from all my fears.",
    "reference": "Psalm 34:4",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470770841072-f978cf4d019e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "31",
    "text": "The steadfast love of the Lord never ceases; his mercies never come to an end; they are new every morning; great is your faithfulness.",
    "reference": "Lamentations 3:22-23",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "ESV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504701954957-2010ec3bcec1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/nature.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "32",
    "text": "Have I not commanded you? Be strong and courageous. Do not be frightened, and do not be dismayed, for the Lord your God is with you wherever you go.",
    "reference": "Joshua 1:9",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "ESV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519681393784-d120267933ba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "33",
    "text": "My flesh and my heart may fail, but God is the strength of my heart and my portion forever.",
    "reference": "Psalm 73:26",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "ESV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506318137071-a8e063b4bec0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "34",
    "text": "Blessed are those who mourn, for they will be comforted.",
    "reference": "Matthew 5:4",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505118380757-91f5f5632de0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/sea.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "35",
    "text": "For nothing will be impossible with God.",
    "reference": "Luke 1:37",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "ESV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1433086966358-54859d0ed716?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "36",
    "text": "We love because he first loved us.",
    "reference": "1 John 4:19",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "blue",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501630834273-4b5604d2ee31?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg1.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "37",
    "text": "The Lord will fight for you; you need only to be still.",
    "reference": "Exodus 14:14",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518531933037-91b2f5f229cc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/nature.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "38",
    "text": "Rejoice in the Lord always. I will say it again: Rejoice!",
    "reference": "Philippians 4:4",
    "theme": "Love",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "orange",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490730141103-6cac27aaab94?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg2.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "39",
    "text": "Wait for the Lord; be strong and take heart and wait for the Lord.",
    "reference": "Psalm 27:14",
    "theme": "Strength",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "purple",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
      "video": "/videos/bg3.mp4"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "40",
    "text": "Your word is a lamp for my feet, a light on my path.",
    "reference": "Psalm 119:105",
    "theme": "Comfort",
    "translation": "NIV",
    "background": "green",
    "media": {
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509316785289-025f5b846b35?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1080&q=80",
